title: Watch Live: Young America's Foundation's 'Rawhide Declassified'
title_page: Watch Live: Young America's Foundation's 'Rawhide Declassified' | Breitbart
text:
Saturday at at 7:15 p.m. ET/4:15 pm PT, the Young America’s Foundation will host a panel discussion called “Rawhide Declassified” featuring six of the military aides to Ronald Reagan, reunited for the first time since the presidency, at the Reagan Ranch Center in Santa Barbara, CA.
The event will be live streamed and will the panel will be moderated by Reagan Ranch Board of Governors member Mark Larson and will feature former aides Rear Admiral James J. Quinn, Colonel José Murrati, Colonel Ron Thomas, Commander William J. Lee, Major General Thomas L. Carter, and Lieutenant Colonel Mark Peterson.
